<h2>CVS</h2>

<p>To check out code from our CVS:

<ol>
<li>To login, use the following command:

<pre>cvs -d :pserver:anonymous@cvs.globus.org:/home/globdev/CVS/gridservices \
login
</pre>

<li>At the password prompt, hit enter.<br><br>

<li>Then check out code from the main trunk:

<pre>
cvs -d :pserver:anonymous@cvs.globus.org:/home/globdev/CVS/gridservices \
co &lt;module&gt;
</pre>
</ol>

Replace <module> with one of the following modules:

<ul>
<li>ogsa
<li>program_execution
<li>data_management
<li>information_services
</ul>

<p>To check out all available modules replace &lt;module&gt; with
"all".</p>

<p>Available CVS tags are:</p>

<ul>
<li>globus_3_0_beta 
<li>globus_3_0_branch
</ul>

